title: 105: Top 3 draft surprises & rookie all-star teams
itunes:title: 105: Top 3 draft surprises & rookie all-star teams
description:
Former NFL Scouts Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks talk about their 3 biggest surprises from the NFL Draft, and reveal their rookie all-star teams for both offense and defense. Then, the guys end with some draft night stories.
